## Features List

- **Normal face swap mode:** This mode swaps the detected face directly into the chosen meme template.
- **Roast Mode:** This mode creates a post from scratch, given user prompt, and makes memes punchier, customizable through a slider.
- **Edit mode:** Users can add, delete, edit filters, color, size, shape of text and their own pictures/emojis.
- **Export:** Can export to socials, messages, text, etc.
- **Multi-face selection support:** Can select and add multiple faces.

