| `compositeImage` matches template dimensions | Template at 1080x1080 | Output image dimensions are exactly 1080x1080 |
| `compositeImage` handles multi-line text alignment | Two-line caption text, center-aligned | Both lines are horizontally centered within the text bounding box |
| `compositeImage` renders emoji in caption | Caption text "fire emoji 🔥 LOL" | Emoji glyph renders visibly in output (not replaced with tofu/box) |
| `compositeImage` handles empty text without crash | Empty string `""` for caption, valid face crop and template | Output image contains composited face on template with no text overlay; no error thrown |
